### Description

Updating Material to 13.3.* the mat-trigger-lables are not working anymore (see screenshots).
Reason for that is that the class "mat-select-trigger" uses table-cell before and no flex is used.

```css
.mat-select-trigger {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  position: relative;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  width: 100%;
}

.mat-select-trigger {
  display: inline-table;
  cursor: pointer;
  position: relative;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

```

